casebody.data:
In re ALEJANDRO R. No. S232240. Supreme Court of California March 9, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, and CUÉLLAR, JJ., concur.

**528The petition for review is granted. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in In re Ricardo P., S230923 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to **529California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court.

KRUGER, J., was absent and did not participate.
